""" Images - uint8 setting/minibatch/augment """
images = Images(['files/0_100.jpg', 'files/1_100.jpg', 'files/2_100.jpg',
    'files/3_100.jpg'], 1, config=['nostore', 'uint8'])
images.split = 0.0
images.augment = True
images.minibatch = 2
g = images.minibatch
for image, label in g:
    self.assertEquals(type(image[0][0][0]), np.float32)
images = Images(['files/0_100.jpg', 'files/1_100.jpg', 'files/2_100.jpg',
    'files/3_100.jpg'], 1, config=['nostore', 'uint8', 'grayscale'])
images.split = 0.0
images.augment = True
images.minibatch = 2
g = images.minibatch
for image, label in g:
    self.assertEquals(type(image[0][0]), np.float32)
